//get ARAD data for Loans to Households
import org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset

val ResidentsLoansToHouseholds_RDD = sc.parallelize(
    IOUtils.toString(
        new URL("https://www.cnb.cz/cnb/STAT.ARADY_PKG.VYSTUP?p_period=1&p_sort=2&p_des=50&p_sestuid=27368&p_uka=1%2C2%2C3%2C4%2C5%2C6%2C7%2C8%2C9%2C10%2C11&p_strid=AABBAF&p_od=201501&p_do=203012&p_lang=EN&p_format=2&p_decsep=."),
        Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))


val ResidentsLoansToHouseholds_DF_string=ResidentsLoansToHouseholds_RDD.toDF()

val ResidentsLoansToHouseholds_DF_int=ResidentsLoansToHouseholds_DF_string.withColumn("_tmp", split($"value", "\\|")).select(
  $"_tmp".getItem(0).as("Date"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(1).as("IND1 Residents loans to households incl NPISHs total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(2).as("IND2 consumer credit to households incl debit balances on current account total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(3).as("IND3 of which debit balances on current accounts total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(4).as("IND4 receivables from payment cards total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(5).as("IND5 consumer credit total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(6).as("IND6 lending to households for house purchase total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(7).as("IND7 of which mortgage loans to households for house purchase total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(8).as("IND8 standard credit from construction savings total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(9).as("IND9 bridging credit from construction savings total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(10).as("IND10 consumer credit on real estate total").cast("Float"),
  $"_tmp".getItem(11).as("IND11 other lending to households total").cast("Float")
).drop("_tmp").filter($"Date" =!= "Date" && $"IND1 Residents loans to households incl NPISHs total".isNotNull)

paragraphs.title: Households Credit Balance Czech Republic
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select *
from (
select 
        Date_YMD
        ,format_number(((`IND1 Residents loans to households incl NPISHs total`/LAG(`IND1 Residents loans to households incl NPISHs total`,12) OVER (ORDER BY Date_YMD))-1)*100,1) as `Households Total Credit Balance - YoY Change (%)`
        ,format_number(((`IND7 of which mortgage loans to households for house purchase total`/LAG(`IND7 of which mortgage loans to households for house purchase total`,12) OVER (ORDER BY Date_YMD))-1)*100,1) as `Mortgage - YoY Change (%)`
        ,format_number(((`IND5 consumer credit total`/LAG(`IND5 consumer credit total`,12) OVER (ORDER BY Date_YMD))-1)*100,1) as `Consumer Credit - YoY Change (%)`
from ResidentsLoansToHouseholds_W) a
where 
    `Households Total Credit Balance - YoY Change (%)` is not null
    and Date_YMD>=date_sub(current_date(),365*2)

paragraphs.title: Households Credit Balance - New Business Volumes
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select *
from (
select 
        Date_YMD
        ,format_number(((`IND1 consumer credit,  loans for house purchase and other loans total`/LAG(`IND1 consumer credit,  loans for house purchase and other loans total`,12) OVER (ORDER BY Date_YMD))-1)*100,1) as `New Households Credit Balance - YoY Change (%)`
        ,format_number(((`IND6 for house purchase total`/LAG(`IND6 for house purchase total`,12) OVER (ORDER BY Date_YMD))-1)*100,1) as `New House Purchase Loans - YoY Change (%)`
        ,format_number(((`IND2 consumer credit total`/LAG(`IND2 consumer credit total`,12) OVER (ORDER BY Date_YMD))-1)*100,1) as `New Consumer Credit - YoY Change (%)`
from NewBusinessVolumes_DF_W) a
where 
    `New Households Credit Balance - YoY Change (%)` is not null
    and Date_YMD>=date_sub(current_date(),365*2)
